summary: An Ordinance approving and confirming the Replat of Lots One (1) and Two (2), Block One (1), and Lots Three (3), Four (4), and Five (5), Block Seven (7), and that portion of the Street included between said Lots 1 and 2, Block 1, and Lots 3, 4 and 5, Block 7, of Interlaken, An Addition to the City of Seattle, executed on the 13th day of July, A. D. 1908, by Interlaken Land Company, John E. Boyer, its President.
